**Overview**

This dashboard offers a summary of the ServiceNow Integration, focusing on general statistics on the ingested knowledge logs.

It provides a detailed breakdown of events by rating, author, workflow state, and topic, giving insights into the key aspects of the data. Additionally, the dashboard presents the distribution of event topics by popularity and event view counts over time.
